    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚的Ruto与Odinga合作，巩固了抓地力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/kenya-s-ruto-teams-up-with-odinga-to-consolidate-grip-on-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托（William Ruto）周五在致命的反政府抗议活动震惊了全国几个月后，与反对派领导人拉拉·奥丁加（Raila Odinga）签署了一项权力共享协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/kenya-s-ruto-teams-up-with-odinga-to-consolidate-grip-on-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 12:48:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利总统候选人伊芙琳·马特斯尼（Evelyn Matthei）揭幕了蓝图</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/evelyn-matthei-unveils-chile-presidential-campaign-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利中央右翼总统候选人伊夫琳·马特斯尼（Evelyn Matthei）承诺要打击犯罪和非法移民，同时在11月大选之前宣布竞选优先事项，同时经济增长增加了一倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/evelyn-matthei-unveils-chile-presidential-campaign-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 12:33:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>犯罪恐惧为拉丁美洲保守派领导人开放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/crime-fears-offer-opening-to-latin-american-conservative-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在整个拉丁美洲，犯罪和不安全感的恐惧为保守派政客提供了促进，许多居民认为他们更适合使自己的国家更安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/crime-fears-offer-opening-to-latin-american-conservative-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 12:05:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普敦促伊朗就核计划进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-urges-iran-to-negotiate-on-nuclear-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统本周致信伊朗领导人阿里·哈梅内伊（Ali Khamenei），敦促伊斯兰共和国进行谈判，并达成一项协议，以防止核武器的发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-urges-iran-to-negotiate-on-nuclear-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 11:51:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的偶然，不合时宜的关税策略播下了混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-s-on-again-off-again-tariff-strategy-sows-confusion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统疯狂的关税弹幕的逆转和错误的推出，使我们的贸易伙伴和企业感到困惑，同时提出了有关其签名政策目标的疑问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-s-on-again-off-again-tariff-strategy-sows-confusion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰在俄罗斯罢工中首次使用法国喷气机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/ukraine-says-russia-hit-energy-targets-in-overnight-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰首次部署了法国Mirage 2000战斗机飞机，以击退今年最大的俄罗斯空中罢工，该罢工针对全国的平民和能源基础设施，过夜。]]></description>
