      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 06:47:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的比特币储备使市场失望，重视加密货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-signs-order-creating-bitcoin-reserve-and-crypto-stockpile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统签署了一项期待已久的命令后，加密货币行业中的镇压紧张局势浮出水面，创造了战略性的比特币储备和其他数字资产的额外库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-signs-order-creating-bitcoin-reserve-and-crypto-stockpile</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 00:54:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
